        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(ci): route Markdown-only PR jobs away from Blacksmith runners",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nMarkdown-only PRs (e.g. `CONTRIBUTING.md`) still queue `preflight` and `security-fast` on Blacksmith-backed runners because the docs-only detection runs inside `preflight` after the runner is already assigned. This wastes Blacksmith capacity and delays CI for simple documentation changes.\n\n## Summary\n\n- Problem: Markdown-only PR CI jobs reserve Blacksmith runners unnecessarily\n- What changed: Added a lightweight `ci_scope` job on `ubuntu-24.04` that runs the existing `detect-docs-changes` action before any Blacksmith-backed job is scheduled. `preflight`, `security-fast`, `pnpm-store-warmup`, and `check-docs` now check the scope gate output and use `ubuntu-24.04` for Markdown-only PRs.\n- What did NOT change: Non-docs CI behavior, `push` event handling (already ignores all `**/*.md`), `workflow_dispatch` routing, and the existing `detect-docs-changes` action logic.\n\nFixes #95089\n\n## Verification\n\n```bash\n$ git diff --check\n(no output — clean)\n\n$ node scripts/check-workflows.mjs\n(exits 0 — no violations)\n\n$ node scripts/run-vitest.mjs test/scripts/ci-workflow-guards.test.ts\n ✓ tooling test/scripts/ci-workflow-guards.test.ts (22 tests) 309ms\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  22 passed (22)\n```\n\n## Impact Assessment\n\n- Scope: CI workflow routing only — no runtime, channel, or agent behavior changes.\n- Downstream: Markdown-only PRs will start CI on `ubuntu-24.04` instead of waiting for Blacksmith capacity. Non-docs PRs are unaffected.\n- Edge cases: `workflow_dispatch` and `push` events continue using existing routing (no scope gate needed).\n\n## Evidence\n\n**Behavior addressed:** Markdown-only PR CI jobs no longer reserve Blacksmith-backed runners; they run on `ubuntu-24.04` instead.\n\n**Environment tested:** Node.js v22.14.0, Linux (WSL2), worktree at `/mnt/g/code/openclaw-worktrees/issue-95089`\n\n**Steps run after the patch:**\n\n```bash\ncd /mnt/g/code/openclaw-worktrees/issue-95089 && node --input-type=module -e \"\nimport { readFileSync } from 'node:fs';\nimport { parse } from 'yaml';\nconst workflow = parse(readFileSync('.github/workflows/ci.yml', 'utf8'));\nconst ciScope = workflow.jobs.ci_scope;\nconst preflight = workflow.jobs.preflight;\nconst securityFast = workflow.jobs['security-fast'];\nconst pnpmWarmup = workflow.jobs['pnpm-store-warmup'];\nconst checkDocs = workflow.jobs['check-docs'];\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify({\n  ci_scope_exists: !!ciScope,\n  ci_scope_runs_on: ciScope?.['runs-on'],\n  ci_scope_has_docs_only_output: !!ciScope?.outputs?.docs_only,\n  preflight_needs_ci_scope: preflight?.needs?.includes('ci_scope'),\n  preflight_runs_on_contains_docs_only_gate: preflight?.['runs-on']?.includes(\\\"needs.ci_scope.outputs.docs_only == 'true'\\\"),\n  preflight_runs_on_contains_ubuntu: preflight?.['runs-on']?.includes('ubuntu-24.04'),\n  preflight_runs_on_contains_blacksmith: preflight?.['runs-on']?.includes('blacksmith-4vcpu-ubuntu-2404'),\n  security_fast_needs_ci_scope: securityFast?.needs?.includes('ci_scope'),\n  security_fast_runs_on_contains_docs_only_gate: securityFast?.['runs-on']?.includes(\\\"needs.ci_scope.outputs.docs_only == 'true'\\\"),\n  pnpm_warmup_runs_on_contains_docs_only_gate: pnpmWarmup?.['runs-on']?.includes(\\\"needs.preflight.outputs.docs_only == 'true'\\\"),\n  check_docs_runs_on_contains_docs_only_gate: checkDocs?.['runs-on']?.includes(\\\"needs.preflight.outputs.docs_only == 'true'\\\")\n}, null, 2));\n\"\n```\n\n**Evidence after fix (console output):**\n\n```text\n{\n  \"ci_scope_exists\": true,\n  \"ci_scope_runs_on\": \"ubuntu-24.04\",\n  \"ci_scope_has_docs_only_output\": true,\n  \"preflight_needs_ci_scope\": true,\n  \"preflight_runs_on_contains_docs_only_gate\": true,\n  \"preflight_runs_on_contains_ubuntu\": true,\n  \"preflight_runs_on_contains_blacksmith\": true,\n  \"security_fast_needs_ci_scope\": true,\n  \"security_fast_runs_on_contains_docs_only_gate\": true,\n  \"pnpm_warmup_runs_on_contains_docs_only_gate\": true,\n  \"check_docs_runs_on_contains_docs_only_gate\": true\n}\n```\n\n**Observed result:** All 11 assertions confirm the scope gate is properly wired: `ci_scope` runs on `ubuntu-24.04`, outputs `docs_only`, and `preflight`/`security-fast`/`pnpm-store-warmup`/`check-docs` all check the gate before choosing a runner.\n\n**Not tested:** Actual CI run with a Markdown-only PR (requires pushing to GitHub). The workflow guard test validates the YAML structure, and the `node -e` verification confirms the parsed routing logic.\n",
